This is the day that you keep how you saw it and I will be chosen.

1245
01:32:07.000 --> 01:32:08.000
I know it.

1246
01:32:08.000 --> 01:32:10.000
As we are getting up to the line.

1247
01:32:10.000 --> 01:32:13.000
As we are preparing to line up I look at my sisters and tell them,

1248
01:32:13.000 --> 01:32:15.000
Go get selected and save me a place in line.

1249
01:32:15.000 --> 01:32:18.000
I will find a way to sneak into the group.

1250
01:32:18.000 --> 01:32:21.000
How you saw it and you keep both of them worried but go out in front.

1251
01:32:21.000 --> 01:32:22.000
The front door and get selected.

1252
01:32:22.000 --> 01:32:25.000
I must find a way to get in line without being detected.

1253
01:32:25.000 --> 01:32:28.000
Meanwhile I am working feverishly to come up with a plan to join them.

1254
01:32:28.000 --> 01:32:31.000
Our barracks are always guarded by capo.

1255
01:32:31.000 --> 01:32:32.000
No matter what.

1256
01:32:32.000 --> 01:32:35.000
My heart races so loudly that I wonder if others can hear it.

1257
01:32:35.000 --> 01:32:37.000
As I try to figure out what to do.

1258
01:32:37.000 --> 01:32:38.000
I don't have much time.

1259
01:32:38.000 --> 01:32:39.000
I must think fast.

1260
01:32:39.000 --> 01:32:43.000
I watch a woman who gives out food from our kitchen as she exits the back of the barrack.

1261
01:32:43.000 --> 01:32:48.000
