1309
01:35:11.000 --> 01:35:14.000
So once again talking about your courage.

1310
01:35:14.000 --> 01:35:16.000
To do that.

1311
01:35:16.000 --> 01:35:18.000
It was unbelievable.

1312
01:35:18.000 --> 01:35:24.000
How this all came to me, how I did it, I don't remember.

1313
01:35:24.000 --> 01:35:26.000
But I did it.

1314
01:35:28.000 --> 01:35:31.000
